      "column_guess": 2
    },
    {
      "block_id": "p3_b9",
      "text": "Scaﬀolds: Triboelectric scaﬀolds leverage the triboelectric eﬀect, where two materials generate charge when rubbed together. These scaﬀolds are espe-",
