        2120,
        2278,
        2154
      ],
      "column_guess": 2
    },
    {
      "block_id": "p3_b10",
      "text": "cially promising for bone and cartilage regeneration, as mechanical movements during joint activity can generate electric stimulation, which promotes",
      "bbox_pt": [
        50.81093978881836,
