        2278,
        2233
      ],
      "column_guess": 2
    },
    {
      "block_id": "p3_b12",
      "text": "highly ﬂexible, biocompatible, and resistant to protein fouling, making them ideal for wearable devices or ﬂexible electronics. They are commonly used",
