        2239,
        2278,
        2272
      ],
      "column_guess": 2
    },
    {
      "block_id": "p3_b13",
      "text": "in bioelectronics and soft robotics, as they can maintain function while enduring repetitive motion. The hydrogel’s conductive properties enable it to",
      "bbox_pt": [
